OL,3,CBereaved families and campaigners call
OL,4,Cfor vital hospice service to repopen
OL,6,FBereaved families and campaigners have
OL,7,Fmade passionate pleas for a long-
OL,8,Fclosed inpatient unit at a local
OL,9,Fhospice to be reopened.
OL,11,FThe 26-bed inpatient unit at Marie
OL,12,FCurie in Woolton, Liverpool, closed in
OL,13,FJuly 2024 due to a shortage in
OL,14,Fspecialised nursing staff.
OL,16,FDozens of people gathered outside
OL,17,FLiverpool Town Hall on 11 March to
OL,18,Fshow their support for the hospice -
OL,19,Fas officials spoke at the city
OL,20,Fcouncil's adult social care and health
OL,21,Fcommittee.
