OL,3,CBereaved families and campaigners call
OL,4,Cfor vital hospice service to repopen
OL,6,FThere's a fear from some campaigners
OL,7,Fthe site will close altogether.
OL,9,FRon's daughter, Lisa, was the last
OL,10,Fperson to be moved from the ward: "The
OL,11,Fcare was brilliant.
OL,13,F"It's important we get this ward
OL,14,Fopened up again.
OL,16,F"There's 26 beds going to waste and
OL,17,Fthe NHS should be using them.
OL,18,FSomething needs to be done and quickly.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/14
