OL,3,CBereaved families and campaigners call
OL,4,Cfor vital hospice service to repopen
OL,6,F"It would be horrible if it closed.
OL,7,FIt's a wonderful service - and it's a
OL,8,Fservice that is being wasted."
OL,10,FMarie works at the hospice and
OL,11,Fsupported the protest: "The staff are
OL,12,Freally passionate to reopen those
OL,13,Fpalliative care beds.
OL,15,F"For the ward not to reopen, would be
OL,16,Fa regressive move for palliative care
OL,17,Fin South Liverpool.
