OL,3,CBereaved families and campaigners call
OL,4,Cfor vital hospice service to repopen
OL,6,F"It's having an impact right across
OL,7,Fthe Liverpool City region because we
OL,8,Fhave so many patients who need to be
OL,9,Fcared for at the hospice and who are
OL,10,Fgoing in to hospices in other areas or
OL,11,Feven going on to corridors in the
OL,12,Facute hospitals.
OL,14,F"We don't want that. We want to care
OL,15,Ffor patients and their families."
OL,17,FCampaigners - trying to secure its
OL,18,Ffuture - also travelled to London to
OL,19,Fdeliver a petition to the charity's
OL,20,Fheadquarters.
