OL,6,FMarie was on one of them: "We took an
OL,7,Fopen letter to the Board of Trustees
OL,8,Fwith the signatures of staff and a
OL,9,Fpetition of thousands of signatures.
OL,11,F"I'm remaining optimistic and hopeful
OL,12,Ffor the people of Liverpool.
OL,14,F"We need excellent palliative care and
OL,15,Fknow we know Marie Curie can provide
OL,16,Fthat."
