OL,6,FA Marie Curie representative said the
OL,7,Fcharity "remains deeply committed to
OL,8,Fproviding specialist palliative and
OL,9,Fend of life care and support to the
OL,10,Fpeople of Liverpool".
OL,12,FMatthew Reed, Marie Curie Chief
OL,13,FExecutive, said he and the wider
OL,14,Forganisation recognised how the
OL,15,F"uncertainty is causing distress" but
OL,16,Fsaid "choices have to be made" as to
OL,17,Fhow resources are best used.
