OL,3,CBereaved families and campaigners call
OL,4,Cfor vital hospice service to repopen
OL,6,FIn the letter, Cllr Kelly said: "I
OL,7,Fhave represented the Woolton area of
OL,8,FLiverpool on the city council for the
OL,9,Fpast 29 years and over that time I
OL,10,Fhave found that the residents of
OL,11,FWoolton hold the Marie Curie hospice
OL,12,Fhere very close to their hearts.
OL,14,F"This is very much borne out by the
OL,15,Ffact that a Marie Curie charity shop
OL,16,Fhas operated within Woolton Village
OL,17,Ffor many years and is well supported
OL,18,Fby people making donations and making
OL,19,Fpurchases.
OL,26,@nD@aOU
