OL,3,CBereaved families and campaigners call
OL,4,Cfor vital hospice service to repopen
OL,6,F"The holistic support and clinical
OL,7,Fcare that is provided by this hospice
OL,8,Fin Woolton is very widely known and
OL,9,Fwarmly appreciated by people in
OL,10,FLiverpool and particularly by the very
OL,11,Fmany people and families who have
OL,12,Fbenefited from the care and warm
OL,13,Fsupport they have received at the very
OL,14,Flowest point in their lives, which is
OL,15,Ftestimony to all of the extremely hard
OL,16,Fworking and very much caring nature of
OL,17,Fthe staff at the hospice."
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@ZO]
