OL,4,Cfor vital hospice service to repopen
OL,6,FCllr Kelly added how the "knowledge
OL,7,Fand passion" show for the hospice is
OL,8,Fseen across Liverpool and paid tribute
OL,9,Fto the fundraising efforts of "the
OL,10,Fmost generous" city.
OL,12,FIn Mr Reed's response to Cllr Kelly,
OL,13,Fhe said: "Marie Curie is totally
OL,14,Fcommitted to continuing investing into
OL,15,Fend-of-life care across Liverpool, and
OL,16,Fwe are very proud to do so.
OL,26,@nD@ZOUoD@LO]qD@_OUrD@NO]uD@JOU
