OL,3,CBereaved families and campaigners call
OL,4,Cfor vital hospice service to repopen
OL,6,F"As with any organisation, choices
OL,7,Fhave to be made as to how the resource
OL,8,Fwe have available is best applied to
OL,9,Fhave the greatest impact across the
OL,10,Fhealth system in Liverpool, and to do
OL,11,Fthat in partnership with the ICB and
OL,12,Fother providers.
OL,14,F"We are totally committed to doing
OL,15,Fthat, and I would be very pleased to
OL,16,Fdiscuss it further with you. We of
OL,17,Fcourse fully understand that the
OL,18,Fcurrent uncertainty is causing
OL,19,Fdistress, and we are also keen to
OL,20,Fresolve it as soon as we can.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
