OL,3,CBereaved families and campaigners call
OL,4,Cfor vital hospice service to repopen
OL,6,F"And that resolution to be part of how
OL,7,Fend-of-life care works across the
OL,8,Fwhole city. In reality we know, and it
OL,9,Ftroubles us, that the care for many
OL,10,Fpeople isn't currently good enough
OL,11,Facross the city and we are committed
OL,12,Fto doing all we can with others to
OL,13,Fresolve that.
OL,15,F""We believe in good end of life care
OL,16,Ffor all."
