OL,3,CBereaved families and campaigners call
OL,4,Cfor vital hospice service to repopen
OL,6,F"I am continuing to work to try and
OL,7,Fsave much-needed in-patient care at
OL,8,Fthe Hospice and will also continue to
OL,9,Fprovide updates."
OL,11,FHundreds of people turned out to
OL,12,Fsupport the demonstration outside the
OL,13,Fthreatened hospice in February.
OL,15,FA long-term decision has yet to be
OL,16,Fmade as to whether the unit can reopen
OL,17,Fwith inpatient beds.
